Class Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.Time
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Time
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Be able to store year, month, day, hour and minute. These attributes can be modified and read. Serializable, so can be saved by Serializer.serialize()!
